name: SMILE Necklace

The charm is 30mm (slightly more than 1") in diameter.

name: Sassy Mouth 6 Greeting Cards-A
description:
Set of 6 Sassy Mouth Greeting Cards and Envelopes.  Each card is blank inside and made with recycled craft paper.

Your set includes:
"So, do I look like I give a rat's ass?'
"Everyone needs a smart-ass, sarcastic friend...I'm so happy to be of service to you."
"We've still got it and nobody wants to see it."
"Age brings wisdom, time heals wounds, blah, blah, blah!"
"I don't go crazy. I am crazy...I just go normal from time to time."
"The proper skirt length is at least two inches below your cellulite."

name: Sassy Mouth 6 Greeting Cards-B
description:
Set of 6 Sassy Mouth Greeting Cards and Envelopes.  Each card is blank inside and made with recycled craft paper.

Your set includes:
"Don't underestimate me, honey! I can go from lady to ghetto in 2.5seconds!"
"I'm looking for a man who can make more than I can spend."
"It's really none of my business...but, tell me everything."
"When I die I want my friends to keep updating my status just to freak people out."
"There are some things better left unsaid...but you can bet that I am going to say them anyway."
"So then they handcuffed me and said, "Anything you say can and will be held against you."  So I said, "Channing Tatum!"

name: Mini Feather Bullet Boutonniere
description:
GypsyLuxe Mini cream feather bullet boutonniere great for the little guy in your wedding or on your favorite coat.  Measures 4" in length.
22 caliber casing and creamy neutral feather plumage make this mini feather bullet boutonniere a lightweight and dashing accent.

Bullet shells & feather plumes make up one fabulous boutineer for the men in your wedding party. Amazing with tuxedoes or casually cool with button down shirt & jeans.

Wether your bou is a military man, avid hunter, survivalist... or just allergic to flowers, he will dig this twist on men's basic wedding style.

Original GypsyLuxe design by one of our very own Jane artists!

name: Rustic "State"ment Art NC
description:
Rustic wooden 9x12in plaque, painted blue & sanded. A "state"ment art piece with secured nails that form the state of North Carolina. The perfect reminder that no matter where you roam, your heart will always be in your home state.

Each "State"ment string art piece is handmade right here in North Carolina.

If you are interested in another state, please contact Jane... it never hurts to ask.
